MathPlayer:
MathJax wisna able tae set up MathPlayer.

Gif MathPlayer isna installed, than ye need tae install it first.
Itherwise, yer securitie settins micht be preventin ActiveX
controls fae rinnin. Uise the Internet Opties eetem unner
the Tuilkist menu n select the Securitie tab, than press the
Custom Level button. Check that the settins fer
'Rin ActiveX Controls', n 'Binarie n screept behaviors'
ar enabled.

Oan the nou ye'll see mistak messages insteid o typeset mathematics
CantCreateXMLParser:
MathJax canna creaut aen XML parser fer MathML. Check that
the 'Screept ActiveX controls maurkit safe fer screeptin' securitie
settin is enabled (uise the Internet Opties eetem in the Tuils menu, n select the Securitie panel, than press the Custom Level button tae check this).

MathML equations will no be able tae be processed bi MathJax
MathMLSingleElement: MathML maun be formed bi ae single element
MathMLRootElement: MathML maun be formed bi ae <math> element, no $1
